üöÄ **Tokenization Platform API Endpoints**

## **Basic Application Routes**
- `GET /` - Welcome message
- `GET /health` - Health check endpoint

## **üìã Admin Routes**
### **Dashboard & System Management**
- `GET /api/admin/dashboard` - Get admin dashboard with statistics
- `GET /api/admin/system-stats` - Get system statistics (DB connections, etc.)
- `GET /api/admin/compliance/overview` - Get compliance overview

### **User Management**
- `GET /api/admin/users` - List users for management (with filtering)
- `PUT /api/admin/users/:user_id` - Update user details (admin only)
- `POST /api/admin/users/:user_id/suspend` - Suspend a user
- `POST /api/admin/users/:user_id/reactivate` - Reactivate a suspended user

### **Project Management**
- `POST /api/admin/projects/:project_id/approve` - Approve a project

### **KYC Management**
- `POST /api/admin/kyc/:kyc_id/force-approve` - Force approve KYC verification

## **üîê KYC & Compliance Routes**
### **KYC Operations**
- `POST /api/kyc/initiate` - Initiate KYC verification process
- `GET /api/kyc/status/:user_id?` - Get KYC status (own or others if admin)
- `POST /api/kyc/review/:kyc_id` - Review KYC submission
- `GET /api/kyc/verifications` - List KYC verifications (with filtering)

### **Document Management**
- `POST /api/kyc/upload-document` - Upload KYC document (multipart form)

### **AML & Compliance**
- `POST /api/kyc/aml-screening` - Perform AML screening
- `GET /api/compliance/profile/:user_id?` - Get compliance profile

## **üè¢ Project Routes**
### **Project CRUD Operations**
- `GET /api/projects` - List projects (with filtering by status, type, etc.)
- `POST /api/projects` - Create new project
- `GET /api/projects/:project_id` - Get specific project details
- `PUT /api/projects/:project_id` - Update project details
- `DELETE /api/projects/:project_id` - Delete project

### **Project Operations**
- `POST /api/projects/:project_id/tokenize` - Tokenize a project
- `GET /api/projects/:project_id/analytics` - Get project analytics

## **üìä Query Parameters & Filtering**

### **Admin User Management (`GET /api/admin/users`)**
- `page` - Page number (default: 1)
- `limit` - Items per page (default: 20, max: 100)
- `status` - Filter by user status (`active`, `inactive`, `suspended`, `pending_verification`)
- `role` - Filter by user role
- `risk_level` - Filter by risk level
- `search` - Search in email, first_name, last_name

### **Project Listing (`GET /api/projects`)**
- `page` - Page number (default: 1)
- `limit` - Items per page (default: 20, max: 100)
- `status` - Filter by project status
- `project_type` - Filter by project type
- `location` - Filter by location
- `min_investment` - Minimum investment amount
- `max_investment` - Maximum investment amount

### **KYC Verifications (`GET /api/kyc/verifications`)**
- `page` - Page number (default: 1)
- `limit` - Items per page (default: 20)
- `status` - Filter by verification status
- `risk_level` - Filter by risk level

## **üîí Permission Requirements**

### **Admin Only:**
- User suspension/reactivation
- Force KYC approval
- System stats access
- User management updates

### **Admin + Moderator:**
- Dashboard access
- Project approval

### **Admin + Compliance Officer:**
- Compliance overview
- KYC review and approval
- AML screening operations
- KYC verifications listing

### **Admin + Project Manager + Developer:**
- Project creation

### **Authenticated Users:**
- Own KYC operations
- Own compliance profile access
- Project listing/viewing

